in adsorption energy studies. Additionally, zero-point energy (ZPE) and energy
difference findings were also investigated. These values were computed by using
the freq keyword in Single Point Energy (SPE) calculation. In addition, in
Gaussian software vibrational frequency, thermal energy, enthalpy, and free
energy data have been obtained by SPE calculations at 298 K and 1 atm
pressure31. The calculated theoretical energy values
